# File Summit_winter_75.amc - am model configuration file for
#
#            site: Summit, Greenland (lat 72.580, lon -38.459)
#          season: winter
#     H2O profile: 75th percentile
#      O3 profile: median
#
# Climatological statistics to produce this model were compiled from
# NASA MERRA-2 reanalysis data for the period 2007-2016.
#
# MERRA references:
#   M. M. Rienecker et al. (2011), MERRA: NASA's Modern-Era Retrospective
#   Analysis for Research and Applications. J. Climate 24:3624.
#
#   A. Molod et al (2015), Development of the GEOS-5 atmospheric general
#   circulation model: evolution from MERRA to MERRA2.  Geoscience Model
#   Development 8:1339. 
#
# MERRA is produced by the NASA/Goddard Global Modeling and Assimilation
# Office (GMAO).  MERRA-2 data are archived and distributed by the Goddard
# Earth Sciences Data and Information Services Center (GES DISC).
#
# Data reference:
#   Global Modeling and Assimilation Office (GMAO) (2015),
#   MERRA-2 inst3_3d_asm_Np: 3d,3-Hourly,Instantaneous,Pressure-Level,
#   Assimilation,Assimilated Meteorological Fields,version 5.12.4,
#   Greenbelt, MD, USA:Goddard Space Flight Center Distributed Active
#   Archive Center (GSFC DAAC),
#   Accessed 2017 Feb 6 at doi:10.5067/QBZ6MG944HW0
?
? Usage:
?  am Summit_winter_75.amc  f_min  f_max  df  zenith_angle  trop_h2o_scale_factor
?
? Example:
?  am Summit_winter_75.amc  0 GHz  300 GHz  10 MHz  0 deg  1.0
?
f %1 %2  %3 %4  %5 %6
output f GHz  tau  tx  Trj K  Tb K
za %7 %8
tol 1e-4

Nscale troposphere h2o %9

T0 2.7 K

layer mesosphere
Pbase 0.1 mbar
Tbase 248.4 K
lineshape Voigt-Kielkopf
column dry_air vmr
column h2o vmr 4.10e-06
column o3 vmr 1.98e-06

